Given a 4 x 4 integer 2D array, <b>arr</b>. What would be the value stored in <b>arr[1][3]</b> after executing the following code for initialization?
</p>
  <p>
    <pre>
int size = 4;  
  
for (int i = 0; i &lt; size; i++) {
    for (int j = 0; j &lt; size; j++) {
        arr[i][j] = size * j + i;
    }
}
</pre>
  </p>
